articles.title: Bloody Shark Rampage in Australia With 3 Swimmers Attacked Over 24 Hours - TMZ
articles.description: Three shark attacks have rocked Sydney, Australia, in a 24-hour period ... leaving one boy fighting for his life after losing both his legs to the jaws of one of the ocean predators, and a man in critical condition after his leg was bitten in the water.
